13. Qg3?! { A big step in the wrong direction. White is attacking only with a Queen. } ( 13.Qxd6 { This was clearly the main move to consider and after } 13...Nxe4 14.Qb4 Qxb4 ( 14...Qc7 15.Rb1↑ ) 15.cxb4 Nc3 { it seems Black has an edge, but White is OK. For example } 16.Bh5 g6 ( 16...Bxc4 17.Re1= ) 17.Bb2= ) ( 13.Bg5= { was also an option with equal chances. } )  Nxe4
